reviewText: my son he enjoyed these videos dvd.  I give it to him Christmas gift.  Hes handicapped child.  He enjoyed to watch these DVD.
Awesome movie for my daughter and it was shipped a little late but worth it for my daughter.
Brought this for my little sister, and she loved it !!!

These are great videos.  They are much better than the old Dora cartoons and the animation and musical songs are great!  These adventures teach Spanish language and good life skills along with cute stories of Dora and her friends.  These are great new movies and my 2yr old loves them!  They keep her attention and she answers along... it's great~!

My daughter loves dogs so this video was an easy choice!  She loves the songs especially - we both end up singing along to them. Also, there is a plot and 4 separate episodes. You won't be sorry if you add this to your collection!

This is perfect for any little Dora fan and includes the following episodes:
Doggie Day!
Magic Land!
Dora Saves Opera Land
Puppet Theater

**I was sent this product in exchange for a honest review. The opinions above are my own.**
